Note: Test file for Runa LSP integration

Type called "Person":
    name as String
    age as Integer

Process called "greet" that takes person as Person returns String:
    Let greeting be "Hello, " + person.name
    Return greeting

Process called "main" that takes nothing returns Integer:
    Let john be Person {
        name: "John Doe",
        age: 30
    }
    
    Let message be greet(john)
    Return 0